data.description: NO BRIDGES, NO LOCKS, AMAZING LOCATION...Nothing but boating to endless sunsets and sunshine. Just minutes down the Underhill Canal with direct access through Tarpon Point. Imagine pulling up to your 65ft dock with 14,000lb lift after a wonderful day boating the Gulf. Walking into the lanai you admire how much space you have around the pool and spa.  Greeting your guests from the double front doors as they pull into the circular driveway creates a warm welcome and as they step though the foyer with touches of wood and stone and continue into the relaxing open living room with a two-story stone fireplace, new LVT flooring, huge windows and sliding doors bringing the outdoors in overlooking the canal, they feel instantly at home. The newly remodeled kitchen with endless granite countertops, a built in wine station and additional sliders fully open up to the pool area is an entertainers dream. At the end of a long day of fun and sun you retreat to the spacious owners suite upstairs and step out onto balcony to enjoy views of the canal. Welcome to waterfront living in Cape Coral!
